The '''Military of Burundi''' consists of the Army and the Gendarmerie. The naval and air units are incorporated within the Army.

Army equipment includes [[BTR-40]], [[Panhard AML]], [[Shorland armoured car]], and [[Walid (armored personnel carrier)|Walid]] armoured vehicles, [[ZPU]]air defence guns, and [[Heckler &amp; Koch G3]] and [[FN MAG]] small arms.

== Small Arms ==
