*9mm Browning\FN [[HP-35]] PSL {{flag|Belgium}}
*9mm [[MAT-49]] SMG {{FRA}}
*[[FN-FAL]] 7.62mm SAR {{flag|Belgium}}
*[[H&amp;K G-3]] 7.62mm AR {{flag|Germany}}
*[[FN-FALO\HBAR]] 7.62mm LMG {{flag|Belgium}}
*[[FN-MAG]] 7.62mm LMG {{flag|Belgium}}
*Browning [[M-1919A-4]] 7.62mm MMG {{USA}}
*Browning [[M-2HB]] 12.7mm HMG {{USA}}

