==== Basque lettering ====
*''[http://www.euskaltzaindia.net/arauak/dok/ProNor0017.htm Basque alphabet according to Euskaltzaindia]
*''[http://www.txikizabalo.org/grafia/ Arquitectura popular y grafía vasca]'', by [[Pablo Zabalo|P.]] and [[Juan Zabalo|J. de Zabalo]], Biblioteca de Cultura Vasca, Editorial Vasca [[Ekin]], Buenos Aires, 1947. Designs for a national typography derived from Medieval and Modern-Age inscriptions.
*''[http://www.lanbroute.com/blog/tipografias-vascas.htm Tipografías vascas]'', a blog post reviewing Basque-style computer fonts.
*''[http://www.terra.es/personal6/landarbaso/tiposletravasca.htm Tipos de letra vasca]'', a list of free downloadable Basque fonts in a personal web page by Landarbaso.
